execute "npm init" in the server folder
go to the server folder and execute "npm install express, cors, mysql2"
create your entry file (index.js) and write call express framework
install also nodemon package (to update automalicaly the server when pres ctrl+s) and add "start" ; "nodemon index.js" in package.json script tag
install the package "sequilize, sequilize-cli" for database request.
execute sequilize init